OL,3,CMouldy food and rats: Children face
OL,4,C'almost-Dickensian' levels of poverty
OL,6,FLaunching the report, Children's
OL,7,FCommissioner for England, Dame Rachel
OL,8,Fde Souza, said children spoke to her
OL,9,Fabout the shame that comes from
OL,10,Fknowing you have less.
OL,12,FHowever, she pointed out that "as one
OL,13,Fof the richest societies in the world,
OL,14,Fit is decision makers who should be
OL,15,Fashamed".
OL,17,FThe latest official estimates, for the
OL,18,Fyear to March 2024, suggest there were
OL,19,Fa record 4.45 million children living
OL,20,Fin poverty in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
