OL,3,CMouldy food and rats: Children face
OL,4,C'almost-Dickensian' levels of poverty
OL,6,FThe government's child poverty unit
OL,7,Fcommissioned the new research and will
OL,8,Fhelp shape its forthcoming child
OL,9,Fpoverty strategy, which is expected in
OL,10,Fthe autumn.
OL,12,FDe Souza said that it is "very clear
OL,13,Fthat any child poverty strategy must
OL,14,Fbe built on the foundation of
OL,15,Fscrapping the two-child limit",
OL,16,Ffollowing calls from a number of
OL,17,Fcharities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
