OL,3,CMouldy food and rats: Children face
OL,4,C'almost-Dickensian' levels of poverty
OL,6,FThe cap, introduced in 2017, prevents
OL,7,Fparents claiming Universal Credit or
OL,8,Fchild tax credits for a third child,
OL,9,Fexcept in very limited circumstances.
OL,11,FYouth organisations argue that 109
OL,12,Fchildren across the UK are pulled into
OL,13,Fpoverty by the two-child cap every
OL,14,Fday, and approximately 350,000
OL,15,Fchildren would be lifted out of
OL,16,Fpoverty at once if it were binned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
