OL,3,CMouldy food and rats: Children face
OL,4,C'almost-Dickensian' levels of poverty
OL,6,FThere are concerns that the recent
OL,7,Fwelfare U-turn by the Government,
OL,8,Fwhich left them with a financial
OL,9,Fblackhole instead of over #5 billion
OL,10,Fin savings, means the two-child
OL,11,Fbenefit cap may be here to stay.
OL,13,FConcerns have been stoked further by
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Bridget
OL,15,FPhillipson's comments over the
OL,16,Fweekend, when she said spending
OL,17,Fdecisions have been made "harder"
OL,18,Fsince changes to welfare reform plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
