OL,6,FEstimates for the cost of scrapping
OL,7,Fthe policy vary, from around #2.6
OL,8,Fbillion to #3.5 billion by 2030.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThe new report, based on the
OL,16,Fexperiences of 128 children across the
OL,17,Fcountry between January and March this
OL,18,Fyear, noted a range of concerns,
OL,19,Fincluding lack of access to quality,
OL,20,Fhealthy food and living in cramped and
OL,21,Fpoor conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
