OL,6,FWhile commending "some positive steps
OL,7,Fby the Government to get more money
OL,8,Finto families' pockets", she urged
OL,9,F"bold, practical measures that break
OL,10,Fthe link between a child's background
OL,11,Fand their opportunities".
OL,13,FIn addition to calling for the two-
OL,14,Fchild benefit limit, Dame Rachel urged
OL,15,Ffor a commitment to a "triple-lock"
OL,16,Ffor uprating all child-related
OL,17,Fbenefits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
