OL,6,FShe also called for additional
OL,7,Fproposals, including free bus travel
OL,8,Ffor all school-age children in
OL,9,FEngland, priority for housing to be
OL,10,Fgiven to children in low-income
OL,11,Fhouseholds, auto-enrolment for free
OL,12,Fschool meals for all eligible
OL,13,Fchildren, improved communication and
OL,14,Fdata-sharing between schools, GPs and
OL,15,Flocal authorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
