OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fare determined to bring down child
OL,8,Fpoverty. We've just announced a new #1
OL,9,Fbillion package to reform crisis
OL,10,Fsupport, including funding to ensure
OL,11,Fthe poorest children do not go hungry
OL,12,Foutside of term time.
OL,14,F"This comes alongside the expansion to
OL,15,Ffree breakfast clubs, investing _39
OL,16,Fbillion in social and affordable
OL,17,Fhousing, increasing the national
OL,18,Fminimum wage and supporting 700,000 of
OL,19,Fthe poorest families by introducing a
OL,20,FFair Repayment Rate on Universal
OL,21,FCredit deductions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
